name: Tetris Worlds [GBA]
description:
Tetris Worlds is an arcade-puzzle game developed by Radical Entertainment, 3d6 Games and Blue Planet Software. It came out on 01-01-2001. THQ published the game. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG.
You can play Tetris Worlds on Xbox, Game Boy Advance, GameCube and PlayStation 2.
